{"type": "article", "id": 44880, "title": "拿“天然”当卖点，这套“画板”化妆品值得一看｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-09-05T22:58:30Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 43553, "name": "nendo"}, {"id": 27564, "name": "Peleg Design"}, {"id": 43834, "name": "Guardner"}, {"id": 43835, "name": "Hayden Martis"}, {"id": 37889, "name": "Pejac"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 115, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170905221647vD57snx8kRZGYgMu.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p6 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font-kerning: none; color: #363636} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。<br></p><h3>Naturaglacé by nendo</h3><p>在公司成立十周年之际，主打有机化妆品的日本公司 <a href=\"https://www.naturaglace.jp/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Naturaglacé</a> 委托设计工作室 <a href=\"http://www.nendo.jp/\" rel=\"nofollow\">nendo</a> 为品牌重新设计了视觉形象。围绕“天然”这一概念，设计团队以产品所使用的原料为灵感，选出 11 种颜色，采取笔刷的形式呈现在白色的包装上，不同的产品则通过配色区分。与绘画的联系还体现在粉底和眼影盒的外观上，这些灰色盒子的左侧有一道浅浅的凹陷，就像是手持画板。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170905221714noDUc7F3w0GYtKCv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562207\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201709052217143aTv8sGom9hYgVXF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.606599\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170905221714ZeVHXsQYDEMJ7glU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.187817\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170905221714n0FfujBOdYg4lsQR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.546108\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201709052217136JkUG4KVfTpONtX2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.753384\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Lemoniere by Gil Cohen</h3><p>厌倦了单纯的手挤，想让淋柠檬汁这件事变得更有趣？曾为 Peleg Design 设计<a href=\"https://www.qdaily.com/articles/38805.html\">女高音海绵架</a>的加拿大设计师 <a href=\"http://www.bigindesign.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Gil Cohen</a> 最近又带来了一款名为 Lemoniere 的厨房用品。从顶端挤出的柠檬汁可以积攒在绿色的洒水壶中，给色拉调味时就像是在浇花草一样。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.peleg-design.com/shop/lemoniere.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>订购，售价为 18 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170905222120DB2IALE3xpkjGo9Q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.623313\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170905222120l9y4oj1NEWRzwiFd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.623313\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170905222120DfWkpMahX6SrENz1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.623313\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170905222119vB5s8uOZCm4KPLdc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.623313\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Room Shampoo by Guardner</h3><p>为了让那些长期卧床、行动不便的老人能够更方便地清洗身体，来自日本福冈县的产品开发公司 <a href=\"https://guardner.jp/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Guardner</a> 研发了这款名为 Room Shampoo 的机器，只要配合家中的吸尘器就可以在不溢水的情况下洗头洗澡。Room Shampoo 的本体相当于一个能够储水的连接装置，一边与吸尘器相连，另一边则是淋浴喷头。开启吸尘器后，在内部负压的作用下，喷头并不会像常规那样直接出水，而是用水雾清洁身体。目前 Room Shampoo 正在日本众筹网站 <a href=\"https://www.makuake.com/project/roomshampoo/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Makuake</a> 上集资，售价从 22680 日元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170905221738PqVcUuEjFwmgDb0a.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170905221739EM9HLZsSPw7vzJR8.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562319\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170905221738i5J2qjBX8HLGAaFV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170905221738NkF1ZYuRE95aLSiA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.629687\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170905221738laPjLzibpBAXuxWf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Ascension Lamp by Hayden Martis</h3><p>圆柱形底座上延伸出一根细线，像一缕烟在空中扭曲——英国设计师 <a href=\"http://www.haydenmartis.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Hayden Martis</a> 用这款 Ascension 台灯为“灯饰能设计得多简洁”给出了一例有趣的示范。Martis 用灵动的线条取代了传统的灯柱，让光线经由歪歪扭扭的“小径”最终投射到墙上。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170905221809OxPHbC2poT6asD7Z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.706875\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170905221808UjeDYAuoGrWcmxOE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201709052218085iHyKwldBNUZxT3G.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170905221808E8eg2QjcadzInSYw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Redemption by Pejac</h3><p>第一眼看到西班牙艺术家 <a href=\"http://www.pejac.es/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Pejac</a> 笔下这组名为 Redemption 的作品时，你或许会把它们认作普通的油画。实际上，它们都是 Pejac 直接在由回收木料压制成的木板上绘制而成的，全程只使用了墨水和铅笔，选择性地保留部分木材原本的纹路，让人产生一种好像全都是画出来的错觉。在 Pejac 看来，这种创作手法就像是给树纹身一样。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017090522182658PkKYhjCVSpasXr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170905221826bXhcufEsYRwvUQ1k.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170905221826C4Mf8kRtd9Xev7uQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170905221827DUZSi4dpgG7LHXKj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Super Hot by Morag Myerscough &amp; Luke Morgan</h3><p>你还记得音乐节上那些奇形怪状的舞台设计吗？对今年前往罗马尼亚布加勒斯特（Bucharest），参加第七届 <a href=\"https://summerwell.ro/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Summer Well</a> 音乐节的游客而言，这个由英国艺术家 <a href=\"http://www.studiomyerscough.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Morag Myerscough</a> 和 <a href=\"http://lukemorgan.co.uk/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Luke Morgan</a> 设计的艺术装置 Super Hot 堪称绝佳的合影背景。明媚的配色让它的森林中显得非常醒目，到了夜晚还自带霓虹效果。顺着楼梯来到平台上方，游客还能发现一个同样色彩斑斓的舞台，背景墙均由两位艺术家亲手绘制。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170905221932ohq7aZCkUiGYuLVE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665037\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201709052219327XyiG05Sro4gUTDx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.138142\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170905221931nikHC7bUzIP8eY0t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170905221931RqY6otOe5iEILPpK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.706601\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}